trans-unit.source: Identifies Windows cryptographic object identifier (OID) groups.
trans-unit.target: 識別 Windows 密碼編譯物件識別碼 (OID) 群組。

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used by the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Oid.FromOidValue%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 這個列舉是由 <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Oid.FromOidValue%2A> 方法所使用。

trans-unit.source: The Windows group that is represented by CRYPT_RDN_ATTR_OID_GROUP_ID.
trans-unit.target: CRYPT_RDN_ATTR_OID_GROUP_ID 代表的 Windows 群組。
